verbose_text: Indeed, reintroduction of either WT or mutant Micu1 in Micu1 -/- MEFs restored normal resting mitochondrial [Ca 2+], indicating that the mutations of residues located in the binding cleft had no major impact on the physiological function of MICU1 (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY C).
